ushions the company\u2019s financials from the heaving cyclicality of deep-sea dry bulk shipping. The company\u2019s management has over the past few years successfully executed</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2187994787/image_2187994787.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747509-dividend-anchor-in-a-sea-of-volatility-genco-shipping-steadfast-strategy", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 20:50:34", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747505", "title": "QQQ: Why Another 83% Tech Crash Should Not Be Ruled Out", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155351397/image_155351397.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Businessman\" data-id=\"155351397\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5616px\" height=\"3744px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155351397/image_155351397.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155351397/image_155351397.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155351397/image_155351397.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155351397/image_155351397.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155351397/image_155351397.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155351397/image_155351397.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155351397/image_155351397.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155351397/image_155351397.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">D-Keine</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>In my last <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4664387-qqq-managing-bubble-risks\">article</a> on the Invesco QQQ Trust (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/QQQ\" title=\"Invesco QQQ Trust ETF\">QQQ</a></span>) in January, I warned of a parabolic rise in tech stocks before the bubble eventually bursts. After rising a further 25%, the risks are now overwhelmingly tilted to the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155351397/image_155351397.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747505-qqq-why-another-83-percent-tech-crash-should-not-be-ruled-out", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 20:36:52", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747504", "title": "Stocks May Melt-Up Like It's 1999", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1031993036/image_1031993036.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Cityscape thailand with investment theme background and stock market chart\" data-id=\"1031993036\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"3092px\" height=\"1739px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1031993036/image_1031993036.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1031993036/image_1031993036.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1031993036/image_1031993036.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1031993036/image_1031993036.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1031993036/image_1031993036.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1031993036/image_1031993036.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1031993036/image_1031993036.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1031993036/image_1031993036.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">primeimages</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The U.S. equity market has delivered two years of enormous returns, with the S&amp;P 500 (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SP500\" title=\"S&amp;P 500 Index\">SP500</a>) up 24.2% and 23.3% in 2023 and 2024, respectively. Now, looking at the performance in 2025, investors may be worried that similar returns may not be sustainable. Indeed, the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1031993036/image_1031993036.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747504-stocks-may-melt-up-like-its-1999", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 20:30:17", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747503", "title": "Major Signals Point To Market Top: Investment Risk Mitigation Is Prudent Now", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1079127056/image_1079127056.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Price crash and bear market\" data-id=\"1079127056\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5354px\" height=\"3569px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1079127056/image_1079127056.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1079127056/image_1079127056.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1079127056/image_1079127056.